body:
@jroper you got it boss. That PR contains my best first shot. There's one scaladoc warning remaining and about 500 javadoc warnings (down from I would guess over a thousand).

As for deprecation, it would be great if you could tell scalac to ignore some deprecations the way you can in javac, but barring that I'm not sure of the solution =(

Would definitely appreciate someone going through the changeset with a fine tooth comb because my eyes did occasionally start to glaze over.
